data.description: Absolute Gem!! This All Brick 3/2 home sits on approximately.54 private acres and is ready for a new owner! Home has an extra concrete for parking. Newer architectural roof. Newer widows and a open concept living. Kitchen and dining combination with a large island and solid surface counter tops. No carpet! Beautiful stone gas log fireplace. For enjoying the outside there is a large screen porch! Home also has an out building wit power for added storage. Priced to sell, call today for a showing this Fabulous home will not last long!
